title: Example Token Launch distribution
body:
This proposal is only an example and will not be counted. You can however use it to test voting or eligibility of voting. A normal proposal would detail the exact token distribution mechanics here, the timeline and the involved mechanisms.
Please also provide a link to the HOPR forum for discussing the proposal: https://forum.hoprnet.org/t/goals-of-the-hopr-token-launch/120
author: 0x8f7a2AbbC8741572427e3426538cD516A41102f3
